SENATE FLOOR VERSION - SB1360 SFLR Page 26
(Bold face denotes Committee Amendments)

1 D. Summer academy programs shall be designed to ensure that
2 participating students successfully complete an advanced
3 mathematical program or grade-level competencies in mathematics to
